title: Web channel (WebChannel v1) with pairing and relay
---
Browser-native WebSocket channel. Dual transport: local (127.0.0.1 direct) and relay (remote wss:// proxy). Pairing handshake: one-time code → bearer token. Optional X25519-ChaCha20-Poly1305 E2E encryption via relay (mirage-crypto already present). Structured event envelopes: user_message, assistant_chunk, assistant_final, tool_call, approval_request. Nullclaw has formal spec (webchannel_v1.json). Needs websocketaf or cohttp upgrade. Integration placement.